  "feesApplyText": "<h2>Tenant Protection</h2>\r \r<p>Propertymade Residential is a proud member of The Property Ombudsman redress scheme, and our Client Money Protection is secured through Propertymark. For more information, please visit the Memberships and Customer Care pages of our website or contact us with your enquiry and we'll be happy to help.</p>\r \r<h2>Tenant Charges/Deposits</h2>\r \r<p>Assured Shorthold Tenancies<br />\rContract Variations at the Tenant's Request (where agreed): \u00a350<br />\rLost Keys or Security Devices: Equal to the cost of replacement<br />\rInterest Payable on Rent More than 14 Days Overdue: 3% above Bank of England base rate<br />\rEarly Termination Request: A charge that doesn't exceed the financial loss for the landlord<br />\rTenancy Deposit: Equivalent to five weeks' rent, increasing to 6 weeks' rent when the annual rent exceeds \u00a350,000<br />\rHolding Deposit: Equivalent to one week's rent at the proposed offer amount. This will contribute towards the initial rent payment upon successful application.</p>\r \r<p>Non-assured Shorthold Tenancies (in addition to above fees)<br />\rTenancy Setup, Referencing & Check-in: \u00a3300<br />   \rRenewal Administration: \u00a3175</p>\r \r<p>All prices are inclusive of VAT.</p>",
